136
00:12:19,155 --> 00:12:23,625
Well...the pain's gone.
How can I just lie here?

137
00:12:23,655 --> 00:12:27,715
That's enough, Dad.
Come here. Get up. Let's go.

138
00:12:27,745 --> 00:12:29,845
Ow, ow, ow...

139
00:12:29,875 --> 00:12:31,425
You said the pain's gone.

140
00:12:31,425 --> 00:12:34,065
It's back
because you're carrying me.

141
00:12:34,065 --> 00:12:37,105
Come on, come on. Easy.

142
00:12:37,465 --> 00:12:38,865
No writing. Enough is enough.

143
00:12:38,895 --> 00:12:39,865
Don't squeeze my arm.

144
00:12:39,865 --> 00:12:42,545
Oh, sorry, sorry.

145
00:12:42,695 --> 00:12:45,385
Sorry. Come on, come on.

146
00:12:46,505 --> 00:12:49,545
Easy. Here, sit down.

147
00:12:50,245 --> 00:12:53,165
Okay. Watch your back and lie down.

148
00:12:53,185 --> 00:12:54,865
Ow, ow, ow...

149
00:12:55,885 --> 00:12:58,465
- My legs. My legs.
- Okay, got it, got it.

150
00:12:58,895 --> 00:13:02,225
Lie down, Dad.
See, all curled up like a shrimp.

151
00:13:02,465 --> 00:13:07,305
- Alright, now. Rest, really, Dad.
- Yeah.

152
00:13:07,665 --> 00:13:08,665
Okay.

153
00:13:14,765 --> 00:13:15,945
Whatchu doing?

154
00:13:17,185 --> 00:13:18,585
Hey, where are you taking that?

155
00:13:18,585 --> 00:13:20,025
I'm putting this away.

156
00:13:20,405 --> 00:13:22,545
You don't need to. I won't write.

157
00:13:23,545 --> 00:13:26,865
I don't believe you.
Let me hold onto it.

158
00:13:26,935 --> 00:13:28,345
When will I get it back?

159
00:13:28,375 --> 00:13:31,905
After you recover. Now, rest.

160
00:13:31,925 --> 00:13:32,465
Sorn.

161
00:13:32,495 --> 00:13:34,675
- I'll hold onto it. Bye.
- Sorn. Sorn.

162
00:13:34,695 --> 00:13:35,695
Sorn.

163
00:13:35,915 --> 00:13:38,505
Sorn. Oh-ho, ow.

164
00:13:41,665 --> 00:13:44,065
I was just on a roll. Dang it.

165
00:13:48,075 --> 00:13:49,505
Here, Pheem, take it. Ready?

166
00:13:49,755 --> 00:13:50,915
- Hey, guys.
- You in, Messi?

167
00:13:53,235 --> 00:13:54,345
I'm not playing today.

168
00:13:56,235 --> 00:13:57,235
Oh?

169
00:13:59,185 --> 00:14:00,395
- What's wrong with him?
- Yeah.

170
00:14:01,845 --> 00:14:03,025
