- Oh, another one.

171
00:14:05,585 --> 00:14:06,985
Guy, I'm sorry.

172
00:14:16,185 --> 00:14:19,145
I'm sorry.
What I said was out of line.

173
00:14:19,755 --> 00:14:21,115
You actually know that?

174
00:14:21,385 --> 00:14:22,655
I got frustrated with Grandpa,

175
00:14:23,465 --> 00:14:24,785
and I took it out on you.

176
00:14:25,405 --> 00:14:26,825
Just as I thought.

177
00:14:28,145 --> 00:14:29,185
That was on me.

178
00:14:30,625 --> 00:14:31,625
I own it.

179
00:14:32,225 --> 00:14:35,145
You know? Some things, once said,
cannot be taken back.

180
00:14:37,465 --> 00:14:38,465
I know.

181
00:14:39,065 --> 00:14:42,185
You said
we came as far as we could.

182
