190
00:15:21,535 --> 00:15:22,535
Yeah.

191
00:15:24,275 --> 00:15:25,275
Can you get up?

192
00:15:26,635 --> 00:15:27,635
Yeah.

193
00:15:57,615 --> 00:15:58,745
Thanks, man.

194
00:16:31,545 --> 00:16:32,545
Take it off.

195
00:16:32,545 --> 00:16:33,545
What?

196
00:16:33,665 --> 00:16:35,385
Your shoe. Take it off.

197
00:16:40,535 --> 00:16:41,535
Ugh.

198
00:16:45,825 --> 00:16:46,945
That toe must come off.

199
00:16:47,145 --> 00:16:48,665
What? Are you serious?

200
00:16:48,845 --> 00:16:50,545
You believed that? Silly.

201
00:16:56,475 --> 00:16:57,965
Aren't you waiting
for the teacher?

202
00:16:59,285 --> 00:17:00,665
Easy. I can handle it.

203
00:17:30,625 --> 00:17:31,625
Whatchu doing?

204
00:17:31,755 --> 00:17:32,945
Uh...

205
00:17:34,385 --> 00:17:35,385
I'm just...

206
00:17:35,825 --> 00:17:36,825
