207
00:17:43,275 --> 00:17:44,905
Oh-oh. Easy, easy.

208
00:17:47,505 --> 00:17:48,505
Ugh...

209
00:18:05,145 --> 00:18:06,145
Oh-oh.

210
00:18:07,295 --> 00:18:08,295
Easy.

211
00:18:39,525 --> 00:18:40,745
Thanks a lot.

212
00:18:41,965 --> 00:18:42,965
Yeah.

213
00:18:46,545 --> 00:18:47,905
