Since when is he your child?

225
00:19:14,305 --> 00:19:16,745
This is on you.
You didn't want him coming.

226
00:19:17,065 --> 00:19:18,465
Got what you want, huh?

227
00:19:21,025 --> 00:19:22,505
Hey, I've got an idea.

228
00:19:23,705 --> 00:19:26,145
- Hello.
- Hi, hi.

229
00:19:26,725 --> 00:19:30,105
Ma'am, these are Sanae Chan sweets
by Auntie Mart.

230
00:19:30,205 --> 00:19:32,265
They're good. Watch, watch.

231
00:19:33,145 --> 00:19:34,705
Hoo.

232
00:19:34,725 --> 00:19:36,385
- Look amazing, let me try.
- Soft and chewy.

233
00:19:36,415 --> 00:19:37,695
Of course.

234
00:19:38,145 --> 00:19:40,025
Watch me, watch.

235
00:19:40,025 --> 00:19:41,385
Oh wow, they're really good.

236
00:19:41,385 --> 00:19:42,985
Made from mochi flour.

237
00:19:42,985 --> 00:19:46,385
Not too sweet.
Healthy-delicious.

238
