Click, pay, done.

239
00:19:49,005 --> 00:19:50,865
Click, click, click now.

240
00:19:50,885 --> 00:19:52,085
Click away...

241
00:19:55,745 --> 00:19:58,065
Well? Is my idea working?

242
00:19:58,065 --> 00:20:00,145
Hehe.

243
00:20:00,445 --> 00:20:03,405
Well, well. Snow could do this too.

244
00:20:03,425 --> 00:20:05,425
