247
00:20:12,685 --> 00:20:18,165
See? This might just be
our daughter's special talent.

248
00:20:18,585 --> 00:20:21,945
Today, we also have
a dance performance.

249
00:20:22,345 --> 00:20:24,465
3, 2, 1.

250
00:20:24,465 --> 00:20:27,905
Sanae Chan sweets by Auntie Mart.

