00:20:38,305 --> 00:20:40,945
Ow, ow, ow.

255
00:20:48,105 --> 00:20:49,345
Ow.

256
00:20:49,605 --> 00:20:50,605
Grandpa.

257
00:20:50,635 --> 00:20:51,635
Ow.

258
