- That one was just me.

614
00:52:02,185 --> 00:52:04,625
- Oh...
- Oh...

615
00:52:05,145 --> 00:52:06,905
I thought it was someone else.

616
00:52:06,925 --> 00:52:08,625
- Yeah, exactly.
- Right.

617
00:52:09,085 --> 00:52:11,865
